1ï¸âƒ£	Loaded raw dataset (Shipping_data.csv)
2ï¸âƒ£	Checked and filled missing values using mode
3ï¸âƒ£	Encoded categorical columns using LabelEncoder
4ï¸âƒ£	Verified data consistency and structure
5ï¸âƒ£	Split dataset into training (80%) and testing (20%) sets
